# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Internal / unused material — keep OFF the public GitHub Pages repo.
# This repo is the public source for resolveproperty.ca, so strategy
# docs, partner lists, drafts, generated render outputs and loose source
# images must never be committed. Only site code, the deploy `public/`
# folder, and finished public ad assets belong here.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------

# Internal docs & plans at repo root (no .md/.pdf/.csv are meant to be tracked)
/*.md
/*.pdf
/*.csv
/01_Website/
/02_Google_Business_Profile/
/03_Marketing/
/04_Compliance/
/strategy-docs/
/resolve-content-to-pdf.skill
# Brand-system V2 handoff folder — local design-pass material only.
/COWORK OUTPUT/

# Internal marketing working files (the finished social kit + generator
# under _marketing are tracked; everything else here stays local-only)
/_marketing/*.md
/_marketing/*.pdf
/_marketing/*.html
/_marketing/*.csv
/_marketing/*.png
/_marketing/*.jpg
/_marketing/Instagram/
/_marketing/cover-images/
/_marketing/video-pipeline/
/_marketing/website/
/_marketing/referral-engine/
/_marketing/meta-ads/
/_marketing/ad-images/output/
/_marketing/ad-images/generate-awareness-suite.mjs
# Duplicate, non-deploying copy of the site public assets
/_marketing/public/*
!/_marketing/public/social-kit/
!/_marketing/public/logo-horizontal.svg

# Loose portrait source photos dropped into src/ (real assets are tracked)
/src/*.jpg
/src/*.jpeg
/src/*.png
!/src/portrait.jpg
!/src/portrait-sweater.jpg
